## NOTES

- All figures in the financial model are in INR mn unless stated otherwise
- Brandzstorm India Marketing Pvt. Ltd. (BIMPL) follows the 'April to March' fi
- The financial model has been prepared Category wise, brand-wise, channel
- Brandzstorm distributes its products through :

| Channel           | Example                     |
|-------------------|-----------------------------|
| Modern Retail     | Shoppers Stop, Lifestyle, Central, Just in \| |
| Traditional Retail| Kapsons, Just in Ti         |
| Online            | Amazon, Flipkart, My       |
| Kiosk (Own)       | Luxxuberanc                 |
| Stores (Own)      | Giordano EBO, KC EBO, L    |

